elements.title: Philippe I, Duke of Orléans
elements.contents: ... that Philippe I, Duke of Orléans, (pictured) was the father of two queens and a French regent, despite preferring his male lovers to his wives?

elements.title: Tom Alberg
elements.contents: ... that Seattle-based Tom Alberg, one of the earliest investors in Amazon, was convinced of the company's promise when he could not find a book by Peter Drucker in his local bookstore?

elements.title: Semi-Detached, Suburban Mr. James
elements.contents: ... that Manfred Mann's 1966 single "Semi-Detached, Suburban Mr. James" was amongst the first songs to utilize the Mellotron?

elements.title: Louisa Shafia

elements.title: Iranian operation to liberate the town of Bostan
